7. RANDOM MATRIX STATISTICS OF Q_k
======================================================================

For large p, the bulk eigenvalues {Q_2,...,Q_m} should follow
some universal distribution. Let's check if it's semicircular,
Marchenko-Pastur, or something else.

  p= 997 (m=498):
    Bulk stats: mean=47.3576, std=545.2808, skew=18.0855
    Level spacing ratio <r> = 0.9626
    (Poisson: <r>≈0.386, GOE: <r>≈0.536, GUE: <r>≈0.603)
